  "dct_description_sm": [
    "New York Metro-North Railroad Stations, 2009 is a point theme representing rail station facilities for the Metro-North Rail Road system, with the exception of stations on the Port Jervis and Pascack Valley lines. Attribute data includes the names of the lines, names of the stations and operating agency. Raw data was acquired from files from the New York State Department of Transportation. Data is provided in the projection NAD83 to align with the NYCMap basemap. The realigned data has not been thoroughly checked for accuracy"
  ],
